default It is intended to create a long term, sustainable economy for Sark based upon an integrated tourist industry.
default&#xa0;
default There is, however, a strong establishment clique which is bitterly opposed to any change on Sark at all, and any investment by the Barclay family in particular.
default&#xa0;
defaultMy clients
default&#xa0;
defaultask me to emphasise that they have no political role
default&#xa0;
defaulton Sark of any kind.
default&#xa0;
default They have no seats in Chief Pleas.
default&#xa0;
default However, they do insist upon transparency and accountability from the elected 
defaultConseillers
default and administrators and work hard to promote the kind of standards which you would accept unquestioningly in the functioning of the House of Commons.
default&#xa0;
defaultAgain I point out the irony that it is my clients who have consistently lobbied the Ministry of Justice to ensure Sark government reform as opposed to the Sark authorities lobbying the Ministry for protection or anything of the sort.
default&#xa0;
defaultIt is unfair to imply, as your statement of general principle does, that my clients have skewed the operation of democratic government.
default&#xa0;
default Quite the contrary is the case.
default&#xa0;
default Without my clients there would be no recognisable democracy on Sark at all.
default&#xa0;
default Again as noted already, the real risk in a small jurisdiction such as Sark is of internal cliques.
default&#xa0;
default I would draw to your attention the fact that there is no constituency system on Sark of any kind.
default&#xa0;
default All 
defaultConseillers
default are elected to represent the whole island; which in reality means that no single 
defaultConseiller
default identifiably represents any given
default&#xa0;
defaultsection of the populace.
default&#xa0;
default There is no sense at all of a 
defaultConseiller
default representing the interests of those whose views he does not share.
default&#xa0;
default My clients' very strong impression is that they are entirely without representation in Chief Pleas; a body which consistently works against their interests.
default&#xa0;
defaultMy clients do require an explanation for the coverage you have given of Sark and why they were given no opportunity to reply and how that omission can be rectified beyond the rather weak proposals put forward by the Clerk to the Committee.
