defaultMy clients have instructed me to write further to you on the subject of your report and the impression it gives that their activities have somehow threatened the ability of democratic government on Sark to operate fairly and robustly.
default&#xa0;
defaultThey
default&#xa0;
defaultsay that this is very far from the truth and have asked me to send to you the attached diagram which they believe summarises the true state of affairs on Sark.
