default&#xa0;
default This is the organisation which runs Barclay affairs on Sark.
default&#xa0;
defaultYou will see that my clients maintain that political power on Sark is in fact held by the unelected 
defaultSeigneur
default, the unelected Seneschal and the Chairman of the General Purposes Committee, Charles Maitland, himself not directly elected by the people of Sark to that position.
default&#xa0;
default My clients point out that they have no influence or control over any of these office holders.
default&#xa0;
